{"tid":143292,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一套對自己刻骨銘心既電影","createTime":"2017-03-04T13:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T01:56:30.000Z","uid":33898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f666b5c9bd0c08007889d20f9d21c569779ace6a","tid":143292,"uid":33898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"我先 復仇勇者(The Revenant)<br />\n係第一次自己去外國旅行<br />\n坐長途機返香港果陣開嚟睇<br />\n望住里安納度係雪地上流浪<br />\n就不斷回憶起旅程既點點滴滴<br />\n記得自己係飛機上面睇咗好耐<br />\n陣感覺一直係心入面迴盪<br />\n直到credit list完咗都未停<br />\n直到依家都仲記得套戲啲對白<br />\n<br />\nWhen there is a storm, and you stand in front of a tree, if you look at it's branches, you swear it will fall; but if you watch the trunk, you will see it's stability."},{"pid":"67d593ee434ece5ea4f0cfc4287aa5b0d7809654","tid":143292,"uid":49912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"Memento<br />\n<br />\n第一次感受到原來講故仔嘅手法可以咁樣拍出黎<br />\n即刻對電影勁有興趣<br />\n<br />\n踏血尋梅<br />\n<br />\n嗰種完場之後嘅孤獨感仲係好強烈<br />\n覺得自己好似俾戲入面啲人上左身咁<br />\n而家諗番起都仲覺得好恐怖"},{"pid":"891dce99b7871186a0a373db7910a20a127617a9","tid":143292,"uid":20898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"家有喜事<br />\n我想刁你個，我想刁你個樣呀<br />\n<br />\n千王之王2000<br />\n仆你個街，亞視黎既喂"},{"pid":"efb4b96b1f5b6c450c679ef134bd9b856ec27c4b","tid":143292,"uid":79373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"The Baader Meinhof Complex<br />\n關於40幾年前西德恐怖分子 內容未算好暴力 不過好心寒  <br />\n有關德國紅軍仲有If not us, who 不過呢套冼白成分太重 口碑冇前頭咁好<br />\n<br />\n仲有Germania Anno Zero 二戰結束後柏林"},{"pid":"24df2db8f179349fe7364310fbebe7579184f7e8","tid":143292,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家有喜事<br />\n我想刁你個，我想刁你個樣呀<br />\n<br />\n千王之王2000<br />\n仆你個街，亞視黎既喂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賭俠先係仆你個街亞視？"},{"pid":"8d00f641729b6d1ea2e9437eccfc45ea163c99b8","tid":143292,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"