d":"aa792822d7b13529b7b66b1f9ec87cff5883af9f","tid":143292,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T00:13:10.000Z","msg":"Avatar<br />\n唔好屌住我先<br />\n我承認呢套可能唔係咁多人鐘意<br />\n但係我好記得我死慳著啲錢去買IMAX飛<br />\n個次係我第一次睇IMAX<br />\n當時我好似去咗第二個境界<br />\n全情投入咗成套戲<br />\n簡直好似身在電影中<br />\n套戲完咗都無法抽離<br />\n好感謝電影人帶咗我去咗一個唔同世界<br />\n估唔到一套電影可以俾到咁美麗嘅感覺 第一次感受到Movie Magic<br />\n就係個次 我愛上咗電影<br />\n<br />\n利申: 之後都有去睇IMAX 個套Gravity 但係完全冇個感覺"},{"pid":"e77a12d7c7708ad0176d33be037112800479b5a0","tid":143292,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T00:38:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">你條女係雞黎呀</span>"},{"pid":"04862da92d1e70468b42eb4e966853cbe42876ca","tid":143292,"uid":18540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T01:01:21.000Z","msg":"兩套得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nInterstellar 同 the theory of everything"},{"pid":"404d8a509358bf306386f57214fb4050ca7feeb2","tid":143292,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩套得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nInterstellar 同 the theory of everything</blockquote><br />\n仲好記得Felicity Jones 係The theory of everything 嘅表演<br />\n真係好值得攞最佳女主"},{"pid":"5ccc024d20903e9e2032036356449b8f6ac4674d","tid":143292,"uid":86578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"幽靈公主得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f18b47d07c1d61f985c3b725f0287887fbd0cf","tid":143292,"uid":63290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"強貼留名"},{"pid":"e46c2c1c0e8b90d3f9b44ffe6d07def72963448d","tid":143292,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T02:57:33.000Z","msg":"28 Days Later"},{"pid":"2646eaa0904ce84689514b799f136fb6ae79504b","tid":143292,"uid":1139,"l